                    {
                        "name": "Blood Frenzy",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The sea devil is not <a aonid=\"15\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">fatigued</a> or already in a frenzy. <b>Trigger</b> The sea devil deals bleed damage to a living creature. <b>Effect</b> The sea devil flies into a frenzy that lasts 1 minute. While frenzied, the sea devil gains a +1 status bonus to attack rolls with its claws and jaws, gains a +4 status bonus to damage rolls with its claws and jaws, gains 15 temporary HP until the end of the frenzy, and takes a -2 status penalty to AC. The sea devil can\u2019t voluntarily stop its frenzy. After its frenzy, the sea devil is <a aonid=\"15\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">fatigued</a>.",
                        "action": {
